  "marks": 1,
  "readingTitle": "tip — Show every step (method marks)",
  "reading": "<p>On a \"use long division\" question the method mark (M1) needs your working to be <strong>visible</strong>: the \\( x^2 \\) term of the quotient and the \\( x^3 + x^2 \\) line of the multiplication must be seen. Write each subtraction on its own line so a single slip costs one mark, not all three.</p>",
